text: Samba Fall (born 7 September 1964), is a Mauritanian Olympic sprinter. Fall competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics held in Barcelona, he entered the 400 metres he finished 8th in his heat so didn't advance to the next round. ==References== Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic athletes of Mauritania Category:Mauritanian male sprinters Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 1992 Summer Olympics
